
Help on command:

	SELECTION

Syntax:

	SELECTION <monster>

	This command allows you to see what a given monster has for 
sale.  It will only work with certain monsters.  After you have a 
selection from the monster, you may use the PURCHASE command to buy one 
of the items.

Example:

: selection registrar

The registrar is currently selling:
1) enrollment verification    7000gp

